Who are the users of the software?
- The users of this software are boba shop business owners who would like to implemnt a pos system at their shop.
What is the purpose of the software?
- The purpose of the software is to make self check out easier for customers.
Where and when will the software be used?
- This will be used at boba shops to make check out more efficient and faster for customer satisfaction.
How does the software work?
- The software works by taking user inputs for their order, storing it in a file, and printing a receipt at the end of it.
Why would anyone want to use the software over existing processes?
- I am sure other POS system exist, mine is specifically made for boba shops, it would let users/customers modify their 
order to the fullest while letting them print out a receipt at the end of it. 
